This plugin provides a high-performance, low-latency Deep Packet Inspection (DPI) engine
for OPNsense, designed for both enterprise and industrial environments under Zero Trust
security principles.

Key Features:
- Real-time deep packet inspection with application-layer payload analysis
- Zero Trust architecture: all traffic is untrusted until verified
- Multiple operation modes: Passive Monitoring, Active Blocking, Learning Mode
- Performance profiles: High Performance, Balanced, High Security, Industrial, Custom
- Comprehensive web-based management interface

Protocol Support:
- Standard: HTTP/HTTPS, FTP, SMTP, DNS, VoIP, P2P
- Industrial: Modbus, DNP3, OPC UA, IEC 61850, EtherNet/IP
- SSL/TLS inspection (configurable)
- Custom protocol signatures

Threat Detection:
- Malware, virus and trojan detection
- SQL injection, XSS and command injection detection
- Script injection and phishing detection
- Cryptocurrency mining detection
- Data exfiltration monitoring
- Botnet detection
- Behavioral anomaly detection
- Zero-day heuristics
- Archive extraction and scanning (ZIP, RAR, etc.)
- Industrial protocol anomaly and SCADA/PLC attack detection

Dashboard:
- Real-time service status and key metrics (packets analyzed, threats detected,
  detection rate, active protocols)
- Interactive charts: protocol distribution, threat types, 24-hour timeline,
  severity distribution, industrial protocol activity
- Leaflet-based geographic map (CartoDB Dark Matter, no API key required)
- GeoIP threat source analysis via ip-api.com (24h server-side cache)
- Global time range selector (last 30s to last 90d)
- Auto-refresh every 60 seconds, manual refresh and JSON export

Security Management (three-tab interface):
- Blocklist: manual IP blocking with pfctl firewall enforcement, search, pagination
- Whitelist: trusted IP exclusion list, search, pagination
- False Positives: review, edit reason, delete and quick-whitelist from alerts

Alerts & Threats:
- Real-time alert table with severity badges (critical/high/medium/low)
- Filtering by severity, threat type, time range and source IP
- Alert export and old-alert cleanup
- Detailed alert view with network information and detection method

Logs:
- Multi-source log aggregation (engine, daemon, detection, alerts, threats, latency)
- Filtering by level, source, time range and search term
- Log statistics by level, configurable auto-refresh (5s–1m) and result limits
- Download and clear log actions

Statistics & Analysis:
- Comprehensive packet, protocol and threat statistics with Chart.js visualizations
- Top source IP identification, CPU/memory/uptime metrics
- Traffic pattern analysis with protocol distribution and export

Industrial Environment Support:
- Microsecond-level latency monitoring and tracking
- SCADA and PLC protocol awareness
- Production-safe operation modes
- Low-latency mode for OT environments

